40
00:03:07,310 --> 00:03:10,810
The coupling constant g
appearing in the vertex

41
00:03:10,810 --> 00:03:13,960
enters into the cross
section through its square.

42
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:19,050
Alpha strong is equal to g^2/(4π),

43
00:03:19,050 --> 00:03:22,850
in analogy to the electromagnetic
fine structure constant alpha.

44
00:03:22,850 --> 00:03:27,070
The interaction has the same strength for
the three colors or

45
00:03:27,070 --> 00:03:29,720
any of their superpositions.

46
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:35,170
So there is invariance under
an overall rotation in color space.

47
00:03:35,170 --> 00:03:41,080
According to Noether's theorem, this
requires a conservation law for colors.

48
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:42,910
