fact that there are many more different

59
00:04:27,185 --> 00:04:31,230
colors for gluons than for quarks.

60
00:04:31,230 --> 00:04:37,420
The vertex with four gluons on
the contrary is proportional to g^2

61
00:04:37,420 --> 00:04:40,883
and thus disfavored with
respect to the other two.

62
00:04:43,918 --> 00:04:49,590
Color does not show up as a quantum number
